text: Katrin Schmidt (born 28 September 1967) is a German badminton player, born in Langenhagen. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona, and in women's doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:German female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Germany Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hanover Region
